OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly fine, with some warm
OL,6,Fsunny spells and light winds, although
OL,7,Fcloud amounts generally increasing as
OL,8,Fthe day progresses. Rain moving
OL,9,Fnorthwards into southern parts of the
OL,10,Fregion by late afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FOvernight a band of rain,
OL,13,Fheavy at times, will spread northwards
OL,14,Fthrough the region. This will start to
OL,15,Fclear and the cloud break up in the
OL,16,Fsouth by the morning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
