OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FA cloudy and unsettled day
OL,6,Fwith showers some of which may be
OL,7,Fheavy at times especially in the south
OL,8,Fof the region. Winds remain light from
OL,9,Fthe northeast.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,12,FUnsettled on bank holiday Monday with
OL,13,Fshowers, occasionally heavy. Tuesday
OL,14,Fand Wednesday look to be cloudy with
OL,15,Fafternoon showers, feeling cooler than
OL,16,Fof late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
